- **Contains**: If all elements of s2 are in s1 but not necessarily the other way around.
- **ContainedBy**: The opposite; if all elements of s1 are in s2, but not necessarily the other way.
- **Disjoint**: No overlap between s1 and s2.
- **Overlap**: Some elements are shared, but not all.
